<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
When MHD_DIGEST_HAS_EXT_ERROR is defined in this project, digest_ext_error(&da) is a macro that expands to the constant (false). Therefore the conditional if (digest_ext_error(&da)) can never be true and the body (ret = MHD_NO;) is unreachable. This constitutes unreachable code (the if-branch cannot be executed).
</scenario>
